---
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-gold font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-3">July 3, 2026</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">The Countdown Is On</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-red mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Two column layout -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-navy">America 250</strong> — the semiquincentennial celebration of the United States — is the most anticipated milestone of our generation. On July 4, 2026, the nation marks its 250th anniversary, and the America 250 celebrations will be felt from coast to coast.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          But the biggest <strong class="text-navy">America 250 event</strong> of all begins the night before in our nation's capital. The All-American Countdown 250 Ball is Washington, D.C.'s premier America 250 gala — a once-in-a-generation black-tie celebration at the legendary Washington Hilton.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          Fifty years ago, the Bicentennial captivated the nation. Now, the <strong class="text-navy">250th anniversary celebration</strong> promises to be even grander. Thousands of guests will gather on the evening of July 3, 2026 for an unforgettable night of patriotism, live entertainment across 4 stages and 6 party zones, and a dramatic midnight countdown launching America's 250th birthday weekend.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-navy">
          Be there when history is made. Join the ultimate America 250 celebration.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl aspect-[4/3]">
          <img
            src="/images/event/great-countdown-pic.png"
            alt="Guests raising champagne glasses during the midnight countdown"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover scale-[1.02]"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-navy/10 rounded-lg -z-10"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
